  "title": "Senior Office Administrator (Facilities)",
  "description": "<p>·  Diploma or Degree in Facilities Management, Engineering, Building Services, or related field.</p><p>·  4-5 years of experience in facilities operations or corporate real estate, preferably within financial or IT-driven environments.</p><p>· Strong technical knowledge of UPS, generator systems, electrical distribution, HVAC, and fire suppression (FM-200/pre-action).</p><p>·   Experience managing door access control and CCTV systems.</p><p>·  Familiarity with vendor management, building management systems (BMS), and compliance reporting.</p><p>· Highly proficient in Microsoft Excel, with strong skills in applying formulas, analysing datasets, and generating reports.</p><p>· Excellent communication and coordination skills, with a proactive and service-oriented mindset.</p><p>·  Ability to work independently and as part of a team.</p>",
